    <item>
      <title>印度增加对燃料的税收，同时保持泵价格稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/india-increases-taxes-on-fuels-while-keeping-pump-prices-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从周二开始，印度将柴油和汽油的税收增加了2卢比，这将有助于在全球原油价格下降的情况下提高其收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/india-increases-taxes-on-fuels-while-keeping-pump-prices-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 10:37:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
