    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯说石油“紧张而动荡”，其主要等级接近50美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/russia-s-flagship-oil-urals-tumbles-toward-50-in-global-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫表示，随着全国的主要出口级在21个月内首次跌至每桶50美元，全球石油价格破坏对俄罗斯经济的影响正在尽最大努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/russia-s-flagship-oil-urals-tumbles-toward-50-in-global-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 09:12:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高空国防股下沉，关税上端供应链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/rheinmetall-sinks-as-europe-defense-stocks-bear-brunt-of-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲的国防和航空航天股票陷入了担心，人们担心美国关税会破坏该行业的供应链，并且随着投资者在该地区一些表现最佳的2025年股票上预订了利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/rheinmetall-sinks-as-europe-defense-stocks-bear-brunt-of-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 08:06:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易者增加了2025次美联储削减的赌注，并有紧急搬迁的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/traders-boost-fed-bets-see-five-more-interest-rate-cuts-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贸易商提高了对美联储今年降低利率的期望；并在中央银行下次会议之前提高了减少的幽灵；随着美国政府的关税激发了对全球衰退的恐惧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/traders-boost-fed-bets-see-five-more-interest-rate-cuts-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 07:11:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票滑到2024年1月，国防暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-stock-futures-drop-after-worst-week-since-march-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股票下跌，自2024年1月以来最低，因为投资者以唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）积极进取的新关税政权发起的全球贸易战的重大经济影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-stock-futures-drop-after-worst-week-since-march-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易商PIN希望在美联储削减：市场包裹时，动荡恶化了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贸易商提高对美联储降低的期望，销售踩踏的股票减少了，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统对互惠关税的截止日期提前几天不断增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易商提高美联储降低赌注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2025-04-06/markets-react-to-us-tariffs-china-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在2025年4月2日在白宫玫瑰园举行的贸易公告活动中签署了一项行政命令，对进口商品征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2025-04-06/markets-react-to-us-tariffs-china-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 18:44:27 GMT</pubDate>
